title: IWeldmentCutListAnnotation.IGetAllCustomProperties
description: Gets the list of available custom properties that could be used for a custom properties column in this weldment cut list table annotation.
returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an array of strings of available custom properties VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
remarks:
Before calling this method, call
IWeldmentCutListAnnotation::GetAllCustomPropertiesCount
to get Count.
The list of available custom properties includes all of the items in the weldment cut list table, which includes items from the file summary items and file custom properties that have been set.
